text: Bischberg is a community in the Upper Franconian district of Bamberg being at the forks of the rivers Regnitz and Main some 5 km west of Bamberg. == Other websites == *Bischberg’s homepage *Förderverein Fränkisches Fischereimuseum (Franconian Fishery Museum Development Association) == References == Category:Bamberg (district)
